    "description": {
      "zh": "一款相当轻便的夜视仪，针对人机工学进行了特别优化，由 L3Harris 公司设计制造。PVS-31A 不仅能在低可视度环境下提供清晰的画面，背景存在明亮光源的情况下也能清晰成像。配有 Butler Creek 物镜保护盖。白磷光成像管版本。",
      "en": "A very lightweight and ergonomic night vision device manufactured by L3Harris. Provides an optimal field of view and a clear image not only in low-light conditions but also in the presence of bright light sources. Equipped with Butler Creek flip-open lens protectors. White Phosphor tubes version."
